Instance: EmsFindings2Fhir
InstanceOf: ConceptMap
Title: "EMS Findings to FHIR Mapping"
Description: "This map shows how the findings section from the EMS Protocol is represented using FHIR."
Usage: #definition
* status = #active
* experimental = false
* name = "EmsFindings2Fhir"
* title = "EMS Findings to FHIR Mapping"

// Commented out to avoid CONCEPTMAP_VS_NOT_A_VS error: sourceUri/targetUri must point to a ValueSet, not a StructureDefinition. See https://github.com/hl7ch/ch-ems/issues/42
